@jeandut
Jeandut, I can understand your answer is not satisfactorily answered. I join you on the quest for nice tutorials.
In the meantime, I got some code running that uses TensorBoard for a nice graph, plots some histograms and the visualization of the 32 filters. You can find it on
http://robromijnders.github.io/tensorflow_basic/

Hope that helps:)
